            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals169"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Improved Grab (Ex):</strong></span> To use this ability, a <a href="ch73s43.html#MonstersAnimals167">tiger</a> must hit with a claw or bite attack. It can then attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity. If it wins the grapple check, it establishes a hold and can rake.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2320224"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals170"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Pounce (Ex):</strong></span> If a <a href="ch73s43.html#MonstersAnimals167">tiger</a> charges a foe, it can make a full attack, including two rake attacks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2320264"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals171"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Rake (Ex):</strong></span> Attack bonus +9 melee, damage 1d8+3.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2320292"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals172"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch73s43.html#MonstersAnimals167">Tigers</a> have a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills55">Balance</a>, <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a>, and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills211">Move Silently</a> checks. *In areas of tall grass or heavy undergrowth, the <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> bonus improves to +8.</p>
